Title: 093: Why Evolutionary Programming Machine Learning is Important
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with Data Scientist at Liquid Biosciences, Beau Walker. You will get a deeper understanding of Evolutionary Programming-Based Machine Learning, you will learn about patents and trade secrets, and hear how Beau went through all his different careers & what choices he made down his career path.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/93
